sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Browser<br/>(PwC FinCrime staff)
    participant S as ACA / Next.js BFF<br/>ca-pwc-showroom-dev-we
    participant E as PwC Entra ID<br/>(corporate tenant)
    participant O as Overwatch ACA<br/>ca-pwc-overwatch-dev-we

    U->>S: GET https://showroom.pwc.com/
    S-->>U: 302 → Entra /authorize (PKCE)
    U->>E: /authorize + code_challenge
    E-->>U: login form
    U->>E: submit @pwc.com credentials
    E-->>U: 302 → ACA /api/auth/callback?code=…
    U->>S: /api/auth/callback?code=…
    S->>E: POST /token (code + code_verifier)
    E-->>S: ID token (oid + groups claim)

    alt Not in FinCrime-Showroom group
        rect rgb(255, 210, 210)
            S-->>U: Friendly "No access" page
        end
    else Group membership confirmed
        rect rgb(220, 245, 220)
            S->>S: Load demo-map.json<br/>filter demos by oid / group OIDs
            S-->>U: /catalog HTML (authorized demo tiles + launchUrls)
            U->>U: Click "Overwatch" tile<br/>window.location.href = launchUrl
        end
    end

    Note over U,S: ── Browser navigates to Overwatch URL (top-level redirect) ──

    U->>O: GET https://ca-pwc-overwatch-dev-we…/
    O-->>U: 302 → Entra /authorize (PKCE, own App Registration)
    U->>E: /authorize + code_challenge<br/>(Entra session cookie already set — silent SSO)
    E-->>U: 302 → Overwatch /api/auth/callback?code=…<br/>(no login form shown)
    U->>O: /api/auth/callback?code=…
    O->>E: POST /token (code + code_verifier)
    E-->>O: ID token (oid + groups claim)

    alt Not in FinCrime-Showroom group
        rect rgb(255, 210, 210)
            O-->>U: Friendly "No access" page
        end
    else Group membership confirmed
        rect rgb(210, 235, 255)
            O-->>U: Overwatch application UI
        end
    end

    Note over S: Startup: image pulled from ACR via Managed Identity<br/>Runtime: stdout/stderr → Log Analytics (both ACA apps)
